<h1>Button</h1>

<header class="wide-container">
  <p>This is the story of a project. I've always been fascinated with hardware. Button is my first hardware project. It's a simple WiFi button that can do anything. Follow along as I learn. <a href="http://button.roon.io/introducing-button" rel="external nofollow">Read the story behind Button.</a></p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <% if @posts.length > 0; post = @posts.first %>
  <h3>The Latest</h3>
  <article>
    <h3><a href="<%= post['url'] %>" rel="external nofollow"><%= post['title'] %></a></h3>
    <%= post['excerpt_html'] %> <a href="<%= post['url'] %>" rel="external nofollow" class="read-on">Read on &rarr;</a>
  </article>
  <% end %>

  <% if @videos.length > 0 %>
  </div>
  <ul id="videos" class="wide-container">
  <% @videos.each do |video| %>
    <li>
      <div class="video">
        <img src="http://placehold.it/16x9">
        <iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/<%= video['id'] %>?byline=0&amp;portrait=0" width="280" height="157" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </li>
  <% end %>
  </ul>
  <div class="container">
  <% end %>

  <h3>Follow Along</h3>
  <p>If you want to follow along, I'll be posting videos and such on <a href="http://twitter.com/thebuttonco" rel="external nofollow">@thebuttonco</a>. You can also follow <a href="http://twitter.com/soffes" rel="external nofollow">@soffes</a> if you want.</p>

  <p>Thanks for listening as I learn.</p>

  <p><a href="http://soff.es"><img src="/assets/sig.svg" alt="Sam Soffes"></a></p>
</div>
